room_title: Escape room "Travel Agency" by Escape Room Park City in Salt Lake City
room_description: You have been selected for the opportunity to be eligible to win a no expense paid trip around the world. If you can figure out where our travel agent Phil Landcaster is, then you can be entered into our grand prize drawing to win the trip. You have 45 minutes until the next group is able to come in and try their luck at the room. Good luck!
